Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,"Pedestrians and vehicles only"\NYou were playing WIXOSS until 4AM this morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I showed it to Grandma,\Nand she got hooked on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoever lost had to peel\Nthe strands off the tangerines, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.60,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, like, how many times did you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:28.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot. You don't\Nneed to battle me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:35.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I figured we can both be Eternal Girls,\Nso that we both can have our wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I don't have any wishes or dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,"Pedestrians and vehicles only"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,--C'mon, let's run!\N--Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:32.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:37.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:48.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:53.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:03.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, finding Selectors is a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.19,Main,,0,0,0,,There aren't many?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At least in school,\Nyou were the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can identify a Selector\Njust by looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIGs are attracted to each other.\NFor example, her over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.16,Main,,0,0,0,,"Special Winter Edition"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"Attractive wears that will beat the cold"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,"Special Winter Edition"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,"Entire Issue★Cute&Cool"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:45.21,Main,,0,0,0,,"Entire Issue★Cute&Cool"\NUrazoe Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:47.58,Main,,0,0,0,,She's really popular now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, she appeared in dramas and it\Nlooks like she'll put out a new song too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl next to her is one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,"Entire Issue★Cute&Cool"\NAh, I see her every so often in magazines too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Her name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's her! Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, seriously? The amateur model,\NAkira, attends Gochu? Seriously...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait? What did you say?\NCan you say it again, please?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Better now than never!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get first dibs and set up\Na match after school, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that... Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:33.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow... Her face is so small.\NAlmost like a tangerine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.72,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.76,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.51,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Please battle me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.77,Main,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.44,Main,,0,0,0,,...a Selector too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,A-A-Are you both one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:54.69,Main,,0,0,0,,How rude. You girls can't\Nget an autograph from Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah? N-No... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for rooting for me!\NYou want my autograph, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go someplace else then. You girls too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira's too generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Unauthorized Access Not Permitted"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,So many Selectors here!\NAkira's so lucky! Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,So let's get a battle done\Nbefore class starts, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,First come, first serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You're first, right? What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! It's a starty-starty of a friendly\Nbattle between Hitoe and Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:28.75,Main,,0,0,0,,When a battlefield is opened, any Eternal Girl\Ncandidates nearby are drawn into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,My hair's going to get all rumpled, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.55,Main,,0,0,0,,It's going to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go first. Battle start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lucky's LRIG is Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}!\NLet's go and stompy-stompy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:05.49,Main,,0,0,0,,A green deck, and a blue deck?\NHitoe may have the upper hand then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Draw! Energy Charge please,\NMidoriko-{\i1}san{\i0}! Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,And, I summon, Sparrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mystic Beast Sparrow" "SIGNI"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparrow, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yikes! That looks strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:33.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It worked...? If I can only just\NGrow Midoriko-{\i1}san {\i0}smoothly then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,That's so scary! Well, I guess\Nlet's Grow then, Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm still scared! I wonder\Nwhat Hitoe has in her hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:52.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's scary, so... let's have\NHitoe throw a card away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:07:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to choose one of your cards,\Nokay? Can you toss it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Spell, Too Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:09.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me see... I bet that it's a level 3 card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Expose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mystic Beast Owl" "SIGNI"\NBull's-eye! Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The card! It vanished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It's one of the strategies for the blue deck.\NThey can force their opponent to discard a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.23,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:27.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}, Grow! And, let's freeze\NHitoe's Sparrow while we're at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop its movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice and frozen!\NIt's nighty-nighty until the next turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mystic Beast Pandan"\NI only have two more cards left... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get too surprised yet! I can still\Ndo {\i1}a lot {\i0}more, isn't that right, Piruluk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Arts, Peeping Analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:08:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have you throw away all the cards of\Nthe level that I'm going to say right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,All?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:08.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I pick...? Level one... Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't good!\NHer expression is giving it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Three... Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:21.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I got it... Throw away your level 4 cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a throw away festival, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:40.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, while we're at it, let me guess\Nwhy Hitoe wants to be an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.28,Main,,0,0,0,,She has no friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:58.16,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got a loner here!\NCan I get your autograph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:02.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! Not yet! The battle is\Nstill going on! Don't listen to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,She's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stop this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! I'll call from the outside, just like how\NKazuki did the last time to stop our battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.93,Main,,0,0,0,,--It won't work.\N--Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki didn't stop the battle\Nthe last time. It was the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:27.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It was an irregular because someone who\Nknew nothing about the cards stepped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.44,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a huge penalty if the\Nbattle is stopped on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:37.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "penalty"?!\NAkira's tactics are a lot worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not breaking any rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This battle's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.63,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I... don't have any Life Cloth left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't give up yet! Guard the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the use? I'm going to lose anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Believe in me, Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:50.19,Main,,0,0,0,,It's over... Akira won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko is the one in pain,\Nbut I gave up... I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.99,Main,,0,0,0,,So, who's going to battle next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a min. Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Sleeping already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's battle tomorrow!\NHere, let's share our email addresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have a mobile...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! Super-rare! How about you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:12.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go until\Nyou share your address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Were you scolded for being tardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I was told to stand in the hall, but then again,\NI didn't have to take math class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:37.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can beat a girl that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, but you still gave\Nher your address anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:45.35,Main,,0,0,0,,What choice did I have?!\NThere's no way we could've gotten away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:47.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I could battle Akira-{\i1}san{\i0}--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't agree to battle, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I was watching from outside,\Nbut Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}was really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But that girl, Hitoe, was strong too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know the Eternal Girl\Ncandidates were this strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I able to win against all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:13.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I know! Yuzuki, why don't\Nyou update your deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,My deck? You mean, go to the card shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never gone to one before. I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.32,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was\Na card shop around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You sure know a lot about cards, Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:46.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've always liked WIXOSS,\Nso I've been playing it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,When I recommended it to Yuzuki,\Nher deck had Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"CARD LUCK" "Trading Card Specialty Store"\N"Dueling Space" "50 Seats Available"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,"Tables Ready"\NThe place feels a bit... mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Dueling" "Tables Ready"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:23.40,Main,,0,0,0,,A new series of WIXOSS just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're here too,\NYuzuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}! It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:32.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We wanted to update Yuzuki's deck.\NDo you mind helping us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'll do anything to help Yuzuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, I love cute girls, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s deck is Red Ambition, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...it should cycle a lot better\Nwith the Adamasphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't the Adamasphere one of\Nthe cards in the new series?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, but there are\Nno singles out on the market yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't get it to pull...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What about these cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a bit of a waste, but they\Ndon't match well with Yuzuki's deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, do you mind if\NI have just this card then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Just a hunch, but I think I can use\Nthis card to search non-colored SIGNIs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Correct! I'm surprised you\Nknew that. You're pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess we just have to wait\Nfor a single to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.19,Main,,0,0,0,,For now, you just have to\Nget better with the deck you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's your turn, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:50.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw this, and charge. Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Can you show me your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You've stopped at level 2 again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You can perform better if you\Nput strategy in Growing you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,This won't do. Your style of battle\Nis too straightforward, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What's so wrong in being straightforward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I'm going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki is Kazuki's bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.17,Main,,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yuzuki"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yuzuki"\NThat's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sisters and brothers can't get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going to say you're bad. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.15,Main,,0,0,0,,"STARCRAYONS"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Straightforward battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:21.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Being straightforward... Being honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.30,Main,,0,0,0,,What's so bad about that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mail Received" "Akira"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mail Received" "Akira"\NAkira...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,"Battle" "I can't wait to battle tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle tomorrow... Yuzu-pon or Ru-ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't lose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You wait here, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:58.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for Hitoe-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder why... For some reason,\NI want to battle Akira-{\i1}san {\i0}too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:22.85,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that's not good, right? I mean,\Neveryone is fighting for their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:37.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Would asking for Grandma to live\Nas long as she can be a wish too, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not with Kazuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He said he had to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not going to get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.99,Main,,0,0,0,,This email says that she'll come to our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:22.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, let's stop by\Nsomeplace and then go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess that's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"Karaoke Do Re Mi ♪"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Karaoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,They're private rooms, and it'll\Nbe hard for Akira to find us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:42.18,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I've never been to karaoke.\NWhat should I sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Just figure it out when we get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, no, no, no! These kinds\Nof things have to be set first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I've got to strategize for the long term!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Strategize?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, because... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the person who\Nwas working at the card shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Momoka-{\i1}san{\i0}, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:09.63,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like that something\Nhad to do with Momoka-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a date--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, you're a bit... different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Like not having any wishes and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You saw that horrible battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:34.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You also saw Hitoe hurt, but it\Ndidn't seem to faze you at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're thinking, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,What I'm thinking...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,That's... probably... right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,P-P-P-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please battle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure what to do since\Nyou were running all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:37.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Finding you here is so Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's battle. It'll be an Aki-rendezvous!\NLet's have fun together! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'll beat you bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I was looking for a way to get some stress off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nodding to the clockwork shadow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}opens the door to the end,{\i0}\N{\i1}bringing in the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There we catch glimpses of the perilous answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's prayer becomes taboo tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upside-down maze reflects{\i0}\N{\i1}the heavens and the earth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The gear begins to turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen carefully among the masses{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:59.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that bell resounding in{\i0}\N{\i1}the skies beckons the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must move forward even beyond eternity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it is the future I chose{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unreachable summer clouds{\i0}\N{\i1}and flickering heat haze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day I'll get back my place of smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't win...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Piruluk-{\i1}tan{\i0}, look into her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The wind feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,"This Nonsensical Peace."
